metadata.name: A pink wind in my head.
metadata.description:
ART - A pink wind in my head.

A creative art collection on the theme of garbage in people's souls and heads includes works representing various sources of emotional garbage. For example, works can depict emotions such as frustration, anxiety, worry, frustration, hopelessness, grief, or fear. 
 The overall goal of this art collection is to make people more aware of the various kinds of emotional garbage that can accumulate in our souls and heads, traumatizing them.
